## Clean Architecture layers (backend)

| Layer | Path | Responsibility |
|-------|------|----------------|
| **Domain** | `domain/services`, `domain/aggregates`, `domain/events`, **`domain/ports/`** | Business rules; **no** tRPC/api-v1 imports; services depend on **persistence ports**, not `@InjectModel` (except Tier-3 migration scripts вҖ” see Remaining debt) |
| **Application** | **`application/use-cases/`**, `application.module.ts` | Orchestration, transaction boundaries; **no** `@nestjs/mongoose`, **no** `trpc/*` imports |
| **Adapters** | **`adapters/`** (mappers, presenters, enrichment, resolvers, rest, trpc scaffold), legacy **`trpc/`**, **`api-v1/`** | Thin transport: validate вҶ’ use case / domain service вҶ’ map вҶ’ `ResourcePermissions` |
| **Infrastructure** | **`infrastructure/persistence/`**, **`infrastructure/auth/`**, **`infrastructure/cron/`**, **`infrastructure/telegram/`**, `domain/models/*` (schemas only) | Mongoose adapters implement ports; OAuth/cookie/cron at edge |
| **Composition root** | `meriter.module.ts`, `domain.module.ts`, `main.ts` | Nest DI only |
| **Cross-cutting** | `common/filters`, `common/interceptors`, `common/schemas` | HTTP envelopes, Sentry, pagination Zod вҖ” not domain |

**Monorepo rings (dependency direction inward):** `web` вҶ’ `libs/shared-types` + tRPC type bridge; `adapters` вҶ’ `application` вҶ’ `domain` + `ports`; `infrastructure` implements `ports`; no `web` вҶ’ `api/apps/meriter/src/**` runtime imports.

### Web layers

| Layer | Path | Role |
|-------|------|------|
| Routes | `app/meriter/**`, `app/a/[token]/` | Thin `*Client.tsx` shells; no business invariants |
| Features | `features/*/` (`features/notifications/` **landed**; `features/favorites/` not yet) | Domain-scoped UI, hooks; consume tRPC + shared-types |
| Design system | `components/atoms|molecules|ui/` | Obsidian Nocturne; В«Р—Р°СҒР»СғРіРёВ» copy |
| Organisms | `components/organisms/` | Shared chrome; notification list may still live here during feature migration |
| Client infra | `lib/trpc/`, `lib/api/`, `contexts/AuthContext.tsx` | Session, query invalidation, routing |

## Dependency rules

### Allowed

| From | To | Notes |
|------|-----|-------|
| `web` | `libs/shared-types`, tRPC `AppRouter` type bridge | No backend runtime in frontend |
| `application/use-cases` | `domain/services`, `domain/ports`, `domain/aggregates` | No `@InjectModel`, no `@nestjs/mongoose` |
| `adapters/trpc|rest` | `application`, `adapters/mappers|presenters` | Thin controllers |
| `infrastructure/*` | implements `domain/ports` | Mongoose in `infrastructure/persistence/` only |
| `domain/*` | `libs/shared-types` allowlist + **`libs/shared-types/src/schemas/**`** subpaths | Zone 6 in ESLint; P0-3 blocks forbidden barrel exports |
| `PermissionRuleEngine` | `PermissionGatesPort` (same class via `useExisting`) | **Never** import `permissions-helper` from domain |

### Forbidden

- `domain/services` вҶ’ `trpc/*`, `api-v1/*`, `adapters/*`
- `domain/services` вҶ’ `application/use-cases` (orchestration is inverted via `domain/ports/*` tokens, wired in [`orchestration-wiring.module.ts`](api/apps/meriter/src/orchestration-wiring.module.ts))
- `application/use-cases` вҶ’ `trpc/*`, `api-v1/*`, `@nestjs/mongoose`
- `infrastructure/**` (except adapter) вҶ’ `api-v1/**`
- `features/A` вҶ’ `features/B` internals (public `index.ts` only)

