## Canonical enrichment path (API responses)

1. Load domain entities вҶ’ 2. Batch fetch users/communities (`UserEnrichmentService`) вҶ’ 3. `EntityMappers.map*ToApi` вҶ’ 4. Router post-processing (transitional Mongo-only fields) вҶ’ 5. `PermissionRuleEngine` allow/deny (via `PermissionGatesPort` Phase 3+) вҶ’ 6. `permissions.presenter` вҶ’ `ResourcePermissions` + i18n keys only вҶ’ 7. Return shared-types DTO.

